# Project context

- Monorepo managed with `pnpm` + Turborepo (`turbo.json`).
- Node version is pinned via `package.json` engines (Node `22.18.0`).
- Apps live under `apps/` (e.g. `apps/client`).

## Common commands

- `pnpm turbo dev`: run the client (Vite)
- `pnpm turbo typecheck`: TypeScript typecheck
- `pnpm turbo lint`: ESLint (auto-fix)
- `pnpm turbo serve`: preview the built app (depends on build)
- `pnpm turbo format`: Prettier (repo-wide)

## Environment variables (repo-wide)

Turborepo declares common env vars (see `turbo.json`), including:
- `GEMINI_API_KEY`, `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`, `OLLAMA_HOST`, `USE_GEMINI`, `NODE_ENV`

